entries.journal_entry_description: Travel just outside of Coronet and call the shuttle using the comlink provided.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Call the shuttle just outside of Coronet.
entries.task02_comm_message_text: I detect multiple hostiles in your area. Take care of them so I can land.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Defeat all Hostiles preventing the shuttle from landing.
entries.task04_comm_message_text: Hostiles no longer detected. I will commence with landing sequence when you give me the signal.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Give the shuttle a call when you are ready.
entries.task07_journal_entry_description: Speak with the smuggler once the shuttle lands.
entries.task08_journal_entry_description: Return the package to the Meatlump Armorer.
